<h4>Forums and Newsgroups</h4>

<p>There is a mailing list mirror of the old mailing list at <a href="http://groups.google.com/group/pygame-mirror-on-google-groups"> google groups mirror</a>. It started mirroring the mailing list in 2008/04/28.</p>

<p>The old mailing list is currently archived by <a href="http://archives.seul.org/pygame/users/"> Seul.org</a>.</p>
